        "rained",
        "has been raining",
        "had been raining",
        "was raining"
      ],
      "correctIndex": 2,
      "explanation": "Длительное действие до другого прошлого события: had been raining."
    },
    {
      "id": "tq_14_08",
      "type": "multipleChoice",
      "question": "Какой маркер НЕ типичен для Past Perfect Continuous?",
      "options": [
        "for three hours",
        "since morning",
        "tomorrow",
        "all day"
      ],
      "correctIndex": 2,
      "explanation": "Tomorrow — маркер будущего времени, не Past Perfect Continuous."
    },
    {
      "id": "tq_14_09",
      "type": "trueFalse",
      "question": "\"By the time she arrived, I had been cooking for two hours\" — правильное предложение.",
